</nav></div></header><main id="main"><section class="grp grp-modules grp-modules-20 grp-768432 grp-bg-hauptfarbe" data-attr-hintergrund="hauptfarbe"><div class="grp-mem grp-mem-20"><h1 style="text-align: center;">HOTEL COSMETICS FROM ADA INTERNATIONAL</h1>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">EXPERIENCE INNOVATIVE HOTEL COSMETICS CLOSE AT HAND</h2>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>Cosmetics have not just emerged recently:</strong> they have been an expression of the spirit of the times and culture in many different forms and facets for thousands of years. We have been part of this history for nearly four decades. We are not only involved in continuing this – but are also developing it further – under the guiding principle of defining hotel cosmetics.<br />
<br />
Thanks to decades of <strong>know-how</strong> and <strong>comprehensive expertise</strong> in modern, effective and well tolerated <strong>beauty products,</strong> we have established ourselves as a leading, trendsetting manufacturer of <strong>hotel cosmetics of premium international quality</strong>.</p>
</div>
</div></section><section class="grp grp-modules grp-modules-54-54 grp-768434 grp-layout-kacheln-gross grp-layout-kacheln grp-bg-hauptfarbe grp-bg-repeat" data-attr-layout="kacheln-gross" data-attr-hintergrund="hauptfarbe"><div class="grp-mem grp-mem-54" data-gal-children="1"><a class="tile tile-gallery tile-gallery-1656039 tile-total-1 tile-withtext" href="/en/brands/luxury-brands/"><div class="tile-text"><h2>Luxury Brands</h2><p>more</p></div><div class="tile-image"><img src="/%28cms%29/media/resize/size=640x480%2Cscale=crop%2Cinterlace=1%2Cquality=70/1656039" alt="Luxury Brands" width="640" height="480" srcset="/%28cms%29/media/resize/size=1280x960%2Cscale=crop%2Cinterlace=1%2Cquality=70/1656039 2x" /></div></a></div><div class="grp-mem grp-mem-54" data-gal-children="1"><a class="tile tile-gallery tile-gallery-1655227 tile-total-1 tile-withtext" href="/en/brands/lifestyle-brands/"><div class="tile-text"><h2>Lifestyle Brands</h2><p>more</p></div><div class="tile-image"><img src="/%28cms%29/media/resize/size=640x480%2Cscale=crop%2Cinterlace=1%2Cquality=70/1655227" alt="Lifestyle Brands" width="640" height="480" srcset="/%28cms%29/media/resize/size=1280x960%2Cscale=crop%2Cinterlace=1%2Cquality=70/1655227 2x" /></div></a></div></section><section class="grp grp-modules grp-modules-20 grp-816172 grp-bg-hauptfarbe grp-bg-repeat" data-attr-hintergrund="hauptfarbe"><div class="grp-mem grp-mem-20"><h2 class="small" style="text-align: center;">FROM INSPIRATION TO INNOVATION:<br />
OUR PORTFOLIO</h2>
<p>Designer fragrances meet sensual scents to improve well-being and natural essences – our portfolio is as wide-ranging as our customers and their guests. A unique, varied range of care products is evolving in the "<strong>Luxury"</strong> and "<strong>Lifestyle" </strong>categories – including trendy <strong>Lifestyle</strong> <strong>concepts</strong>, well-known licence and designer brands and wellness-oriented lines, certified natural cosmetics or products with fair trade essences. The birth of our company simultaneously marks the start of the development of a completely new product concept: personalised <strong>hotel cosmetics</strong> give your business an individual flavour, its own handwriting – as individual and unmistakable as your hotel.</p>
<p>The latest chapter in the history of hotel cosmetics is focussing on the development of ecological concepts. <strong>ADA International</strong> is also a leading player here. With a wide range of environmentally friendly and cost-effective dispenser systems with equally impressive high quality, functionality and design strength, we can strike a balance between <strong>exclusivity, elegance and sustainability</strong>.</p>
</div></section><section class="grp grp-modules grp-modules-20 grp-768437 grp-bg-world_map" data-attr-hintergrund="world_map"><div class="grp-mem grp-mem-20"><h2>ADA Sales Representatives</h2>
<p>We are located in more than 50 countries with an international distribution network and a large number of sales partners – a fact our clients really appreciate. We do, however, offer more than just geographic proximity. Our partner network enables us to combine local market knowledge with international market experience for the benefit of our clients. Thus, we can guarantee products that meet country-specific requirements and, in addition, set high international standards.</p>
